{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f42ff7ed20","title":"各中央局、分局、前委应向中央报告的事项","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"02f3fb085a","index":0,"year":1948,"month":6,"day":25,"articleId":"f42ff7ed20","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji5","name":"毛泽东文集第五卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji5.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji5":{"comments":[{"id":"71649826c6","publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"ee18ddff0e","publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":10,"offset":18,"text":"三查三整，见本卷第47页注〔3〕。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f278aab76f","type":"title","text":"各中央局、分局、前委应向中央报告的事项","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee18ddff0e","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，分局，前委：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96f4f65fdc","type":"paragraph","text":"下列各项，嗣后必须在事先或事后报告中央，经中央审查批准已在执行中者，除业已呈报者外，须将指示或决议或条例或命令补行呈报备审。（一）税收政策，内分农业税（即公粮）、工业税、商业税。（二）工资政策，内分公营企业工资、民营企业工资（包括合作社）、乡村工资。（三）每年财政预算。（四）全区脱离生产人员的数量和人口数量的比例。（五）每年动员新兵计划。（六）增加新的团、旅（师）及纵队的数量及编制。（七）全区每年土改工作范围、政策及干部配备。（八）全区生产计划、投资及贷款计划，内分工业、交通、矿业、航业、农业及商业。（九）货币政策及发行计划。（十）外交政策、外交事件之处理及外人宗教案件之处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc489bfe79","type":"paragraph","text":"（十一）文化教育政策，全区文教事业计划。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd9e152bfe","type":"paragraph","text":"（十二）高级人民代表会议及高级政府组成中我党与他党及非党人员的配备。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba759370ab","type":"paragraph","text":"（十三）我党与民主党派及非党人员合作的政策。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a115acc2da","type":"paragraph","text":"（十四）全区司法政策，即如何对待各类犯罪分子。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"37e027483f","type":"paragraph","text":"（十五）党校及军校的计划及教育方针。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"afd5e851d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（十六）区党委或省委的书记、副书记及委员的配备。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d1c8902c8","type":"paragraph","text":"（十七）旅（或师）一级及其以上各级主要人员的配备。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e5a64893e2","type":"paragraph","text":"（十八）整党计划及政策（包括三查三整在内）。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"185f0bd9c1","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":11,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6578df24eb","type":"paragraph","text":"巳有","index":12,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"f42ff7ed20","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":121,"end":120}}}},"__N_SSG":true}